      <title>比亚迪宣布回购新股并计划推出更多豪华车型</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/byd-announces-new-stock-buyback-and-plans-more-luxury-models</link>
      <description><![CDATA[比亚迪公司在周日提交的一份文件中表示，该公司计划回购更多股票，以扭转本月初跌至 15 个月低点的股价暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/byd-announces-new-stock-buyback-and-plans-more-luxury-models</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 02:08:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新加坡计划征收可持续燃油税，这将推高机票价格</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/singapore-plans-sustainable-fuel-levy-that-will-push-up-airfares</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新加坡计划对机票征税，以支付可持续航空燃料的费用，这是该行业脱碳努力将如何增加旅行成本的早期迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/singapore-plans-sustainable-fuel-levy-that-will-push-up-airfares</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 01:59:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>软银股价因 CEO 计划 1000 亿美元芯片项目而上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/softbank-stock-rises-on-ceo-s-plan-for-100-billion-chip-project</link>
      <description><![CDATA[软银集团 (SoftBank Group Corp.) 创始人孙正义 (Masayoshi Son) 考虑创建一家价值 1000 亿美元的芯片企业，供应人工智能半导体，其股价上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/softbank-stock-rises-on-ceo-s-plan-for-100-billion-chip-project</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 01:00:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>游戏制造商表示 Switch 2 推迟到 2025 年发售，任天堂陷入困境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/nintendo-plunges-after-game-makers-say-switch-2-pushed-to-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[有报道称任天堂公司将 Switch 继任者的发布推迟到明年初，随后该公司股价应声暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/nintendo-plunges-after-game-makers-say-switch-2-pushed-to-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 00:13:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚马逊正在制作一部罗杰·费德勒纪录片，更深入地涉足体育领域</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-02-18/amazon-is-making-a-roger-federer-documentary-moving-deeper-into-sports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[这位网球巨星以为他正在制作一部关于他职业生涯最后 12 天的家庭电影。它由屡获殊荣的电影制作人阿西夫·卡帕迪亚 (Asif Kapadia) 改编成纪录片。]]></description>
